<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pengaturan Produk</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        th, td { padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle;}
        th { background-color: #f2f2f2; }
        .sync-form button { padding: 10px 15px; background-color: #1a237e; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 20px;}
        .toggle-form button { padding: 5px 10px; width: 100px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; color: white; cursor: pointer; }
        .toggle-form .active { background-color: #4CAF50; /* Green */ }
        .toggle-form .inactive { background-color: #f44336; /* Red */ }
        .image-form { display: flex; gap: 5px; }
        .image-form input { flex-grow: 1; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>⚙️ Pengaturan Produk</h1>
        <p><a href="/admin/dashboard" style="color: white;">Kembali ke Dashboard</a></p>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Sinkronisasi dengan Digiflazz</h2>
            <p>Klik tombol di bawah untuk mengambil daftar produk terbaru dari Digiflazz. Produk baru akan ditambahkan ke daftar di bawah dalam keadaan nonaktif.</p>
            <form class="sync-form" action="/admin/sync-digiflazz" method="POST">
                <button type="submit">Sinkronkan Sekarang</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Daftar Produk</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Brand</th>
                        <th>Kategori</th>
                        <th>Gambar</th>
                        <th>Status Aktif</th>
                        <th>Status Populer</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% products.forEach(product => { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong><%= product.brand %></strong></td>
                            <td><%= product.category %></td>
                            <td>
                                <form action="/admin/products/update-image/<%= product.id %>" method="POST" class="image-form">
                                    <input type="text" name="imageUrl" placeholder="URL Gambar" value="<%= product.imageUrl || '' %>">
                                    <button type="submit">Simpan</button>
                                </form>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <form action="/admin/products/toggle-active/<%= product.id %>" method="POST" class="toggle-form">
                                    <button type="submit" class="<%= product.isActive ? 'active' : 'inactive' %>">
                                        <%= product.isActive ? 'Aktif' : 'Nonaktif' %>
                                    </button>
                                </form>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <form action="/admin/products/toggle-popular/<%= product.id %>" method="POST" class="toggle-form">
                                    <button type="submit" class="<%= product.isPopular ? 'active' : 'inactive' %>">
                                        <%= product.isPopular ? 'Populer' : 'Biasa' %>
                                    </button>
                                </form>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    <% }) %>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>